        <div class="fitting-guide__description-wrapper">
            <div class="fitting-guide__description">
                <h2 class="section-heading">How to Measure</h2>
                <p class="fitting-guide__description-subheading">1.Bust:</p>
                <p>Using soft measuring tape, measure completely around the fullest part of the bust. Take a deep breath in and out to make sure the tape isnâ€™t too tight or too loose.</p>
                <p class="fitting-guide__description-subheading">2.Waist:</p>
                <p>Measure the narrowest part of the waist.</p>
                <p class="fitting-guide__description-subheading">3.Hip 1:</p>
                <p>Measure the circumference of the hips 6" up from the crotch.</p>
                <p class="fitting-guide__description-subheading">4.Hip 2:</p>
                <p>Stand with your feet together, and identify the point of your hip that is level with your crotch. Measure the circumference of this area.</p>
            </div>
